{"id":"3595","name":"you-tell-us-home-of-the-best-hot-chocolate-nashvillest-polls","title":"You Tell Us: Home Of The Best Hot Chocolate? [Nashvillest Polls]","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2010-01-06T16:00:00-06:00","tags":["cocoa","hot chocolate","nashvillest polls","the cocoa tree","you tell us"],"categories":["Featured","Food &amp; Drink"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3487/3192038647_b36071c996.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p>It&#x2019;s so cold outside, we&#x2019;re doing everything we can to stay warm. We&#x2019;ve asked you about your <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/28/you-tell-us-whats-your-favorite-warm-winter-drink-in-town/\" target=\"_blank\">favorite belly-warming wintery drinks</a> before, but now we&#x2019;re on a quest to hunt down the best cup of hot chocolate in town (thanks to a query by our friend <a href=\"http://twitter.com/justwinston/status/7453865278\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;twitter.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Winston</a>). Responses have been pouring in on Twitter, with <a href=\"http://www.thecocoatree.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.thecocoatree.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Cocoa Tree</a> emerging as a clear leader &#x2013; But don&#x2019;t let that sway your vote!</p><p><strong>So tell us, what&#x2019;s the best cup o&#x2019;cocoa in town?</strong> (If we left your favorite off the list, a thousand apologies, but that&#x2019;s why the &#x201C;Other&#x201D; option is there.)</p><div id=\"polls-12\" class=\"wp-polls\">\t<form id=\"polls_form_12\" class=\"wp-polls-form\" action=\"/2010/01/06/you-tell-us-home-of-the-best-hot-chocolate-nashvillest-polls/\" method=\"post\">\t\t<p style=\"display: none;\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"poll_id\" value=\"12\"></p>\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>What&apos;s the best cup o&apos;cocoa in Nashville?</strong></p><div id=\"polls-12-ans\" class=\"wp-polls-ans\"><ul class=\"wp-polls-ul\">\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-77\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"77\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-77\">The Cocoa Tree</label></li>\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-78\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"78\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-78\">Portland Brew</label></li>\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-79\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"79\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-79\">Frothy Monkey</label></li>\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-80\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"80\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-80\">Bongo Java</label></li>\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" id=\"poll-answer-81\" name=\"poll_12\" value=\"81\"> <label for=\"poll-answer-81\">Mike&apos;s Ice Cream Fountain</label></li>\t\t<li><input type=\"radio\" i